		===================================
		libavfltctl - AVFlt Control Library
			       README
		===================================

This software is distributed under the Boost Software License, Version 1.0.

1. Introduction

	AVFlt Control Library is a userspace library, which provides interface
	for basic management of AVFlt. It extends functionality of the librfsctl
	library for options specific for AVFlt.

	For an overview of the RedirFS project, visit 

		http://www.redirfs.org

2. Installation

	See the INSTALL file.

3. Documentation

	http://www.redirfs.org/tiki-index.php?page=redirfs_doc

4. Problems & Bugs
	
	http://www.redirfs.org/cgi-bin/bugzilla/index.cgi
